<br>
This is my dad's character on the Drinal Server. I myself play a 65 monk on Rallos Zek.<br>
<br>
Anyway. My dad's character has never been given very many opportunities for gear, cash, etc. Tinkering is taking up what little money Binbi can make, and the character isn't getting much in return from selling on the bazaar.<br>
<br>
So Here's what I happily request. Please take a VERY careful look at her gear.<br>
<br>
Binbi has a budget of 2300 plat. She has VERY minor skill in 1hb, 2hb, and peircing.<br>
<br>
She's in a dying guild, or to say the least a very innactive guild, so raiding isn't very much of an opportunity.<br>
(Hell, a great majority of the Lords of Ters'Tai guild hasn't even logged on since the release of Legacy of Ykesha.)<br>
<br>
I do know this much:<br>
<br>
When she can get a group (which isn't very often), she's usually not the tank character.<br>
<br>
Neck Slot: Sapphire Velium Necklace. I can only imagine the only reason she's using it is for tradeskills, which makes sense.. however its also the best she's got for battle gear.<br>
<br>
HASTE ITEM SEVERLY NEEDED!<br>
<br>
For the majority, she's still wearing Crafted armor.. the mid-level warrior armor introduced before Kunark came out.<br>
<br>
An upgrade from a Strength of Grodan for a 2hs weapon wouldn't hurt.<br>
<br>
An Upgrade on 1hs weapons wouldn't hurt either.<br>
<br>
Please give your suggestions. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showPrevMessage?topicID=5552.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showNextMessage?topicID=5552.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=5552.topic><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.emailToFriend?topicID=5552.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.threadControl?topicID=5552.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5552.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=5552.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub14.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesteelwarriorthearena">The Arena<option value="thesteelwarriorthebattlefield">The BattleField<option value="thesteelwarriorthebunker">The Bunker<option value="thesteelwarriorthetavern">The Tavern<option value="thest